               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>A complete copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Tiruvātavūrār Purāṇam</title>, entitled here <title xml:lang="ta">Vātavūrar purāṇam</title>, a poem on the life of <persName>Māṇikkavācakar</persName>, by <persName role="author">Kaṭavuṇmāmuṉivar</persName> (15th century?). See Sweetman &amp; Ilakkuvan (2012, p. 66), Zvelebil (1995, p. 334, 405).</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (March 2023).</p> 
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p></summary>
                  
